00:00:07.656 --> 00:00:09.962
 Welcome to the Supermaster Series Video Guide 

00:00:10.452 --> 00:00:12.893
 Crown on the side edge of the watch 

00:00:13.013 --> 00:00:16.067
 Can be used to set the time and wind up the watch 

00:00:16.567 --> 00:00:18.292
 Every day, the watch is fully chained once 

00:00:18.412 --> 00:00:21.161
 Can ensure that the watch is working properly 

00:00:21.281 --> 00:00:22.423
 To wind the watch 

00:00:22.543 --> 00:00:25.229
 Rotate the crown forward until it stops 

00:00:28.037 --> 00:00:29.205
 To set the time 

00:00:29.325 --> 00:00:32.241
 Pull the crown out until you hear a click 

00:00:33.612 --> 00:00:35.709
 Rotate the crown forward or backward 

00:00:35.933 --> 00:00:38.869
 Move the hour and minute hands to the desired time 

00:00:42.315 --> 00:00:44.004
 After setting is completed 

00:00:44.124 --> 00:00:46.372
 Please make sure to press the crown back to position 1 

00:00:49.154 --> 00:00:51.678
 Timing device can be used 

00:00:51.798 --> 00:00:53.305
 Measure up to 12 hours 

00:00:54.602 --> 00:00:56.393
 To start or stop timing 

00:00:56.513 --> 00:00:59.150
 Just press the top button at 2 o'clock 

00:01:08.704 --> 00:01:10.415
 To reset the chronograph pointer 

00:01:10.535 --> 00:01:13.025
 Just press the button below the 4 o'clock position 

00:01:21.271 --> 00:01:23.461
 To facilitate reading time in dimly lit environments 

00:01:23.581 --> 00:01:25.527
 Pointer and scale of the watch 

00:01:25.647 --> 00:01:27.185
 Both are coated with luminous coating 

00:01:27.305 --> 00:01:29.063
 Can emit green light 

00:01:35.949 --> 00:01:37.694
 Through the central timing indicator 

00:01:37.814 --> 00:01:39.592
 And the speed scale of the watch 

00:01:39.712 --> 00:01:41.548
 Super watch can be measured 

00:01:41.668 --> 00:01:44.078
 Average moving speed of the object 

00:01:44.624 --> 00:01:46.366
 Such as the speed of the vehicle 

00:01:46.486 --> 00:01:49.269
 Can make measurements by the time required to drive one kilometer 

00:01:49.963 --> 00:01:52.414
 Just press the top button at 2 o'clock 

00:01:52.534 --> 00:01:54.021
 start the timer 

00:01:55.485 --> 00:01:58.082
 When the vehicle walks for one kilometer 

00:01:58.202 --> 00:02:00.538
 Press the button again to stop timing 

00:02:00.658 --> 00:02:02.962
 Then read the values ​​on the bezel scale 

00:02:05.086 --> 00:02:08.209
 In this example the vehicle is running in 30 seconds. 

00:02:08.522 --> 00:02:09.419
 therefore 

00:02:09.539 --> 00:02:13.227
 The average speed of the vehicle is 120 kilometers per hour. 

00:02:16.871 --> 00:02:18.759
 Thank you for watching this video guide. 

00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:21.088
 I hope you like your Super Watch. 

